<BaseLayout title="CNC vs 3D Printing | CNC与3D打印对比">

<h1>
CNC vs 3D Printing
</h1>

<p>
CNC适合高强度与精度零件，3D打印适合复杂结构原型
</p>

<h2>When to use CNC</h2>
<ul>
  <li>High strength parts</li>
  <li>Precision requirements</li>
</ul>

<h2>When to use 3D Printing</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Complex geometry</li>
  <li>Fast prototyping</li>
</ul>

</BaseLayout>